{
  "title": "Buttery Malaysian Duck Legs Roast",
  "description": "A crumbly, buttery roast of duck legs with a hint of Malaysian spices, perfect for midnight cravings. Low-sodium version keeps it healthy without sacrificing flavor.",
  "cuisine": "malaysian",
  "diet": [
    "low-sodium",
